lead_paragraph: Former Welsh footballer turned soccer pundit Dean Saunders will have to do better than hunt around his glove box or down the back of the seats for coins to pay for parking when he finally returns from the European Championship.

headline.print_headline: Oh Ye of Little Faith! Deano's Parking Woe
